---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Colophon" description="How this site is built.">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>Colophon</h1>
    <p>
      Built with <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a>.
      Styled with <a href="https://tailwindcss.com">Tailwind CSS</a>.
      Hosted on <a href="https://vercel.com">Vercel</a>.
      Content lives in Markdown, managed through Astro's content collections.
    </p>
    <p>
      Headings are set in <a href="https://github.com/cyrealtype/Lora">Lora</a>.
      Body text is <a href="https://rsms.me/inter/">Inter</a>.
      Code is <a href="https://www.jetbrains.com/lp/mono/">JetBrains Mono</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Fast, quiet, readable. No tracking. No cookie banners. Just the work.
    </p>
    <p>
      Source on <a href="https://github.com/Fluxuous/parkerferguson-dot-xyz">GitHub</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
